title: Midway Chamber endorses St. Paul soccer stadium
text:
Home / Brief / Midway Chamber endorses St. Paul soccer stadium Midway Chamber endorses St. Paul soccer stadium By: Karlee Weinmann September 23, 2015 6:23 pm 0 The Midway Chamber of Commerce this week threw its weight behind plans to bring a Major League Soccer stadium to St. Paul. After going months without taking an official stance, the group said Tuesday afternoon the $120 million-plus facility would bolster surrounding businesses.
